movieDescription: Movie story revolves around two bad guys who struggle with forces of good and evil while exploring the psychological secret that people tend to bury deep within their minds. The film reveals dark secrets, which manifest into a series of attacks that seek to destroy. It’s about the happening incidents in 24 hours involving crime investigation.

Movie story start with Balu loses his parents at a very young age and all his relatives leave him alone in life. Upset with this he starts an emotion supplier business with his friend. The concept of their company is to send people as close relatives and remove all the problems in their lives. In one case, Balu goes as a son to Tanikella Bharani’s house and gets into deep trouble featuring a sand mafia kingpin.
staring: Kalyan Ram, Mehreen Pirzada, Vennela Kishore

movieDescription: Movie is about Devadas is born with a fatal alcoholic syndrome and needs to drink 90 ML liquor three times a day to survive. He falls in love with Suvasana who hates alcohol. The twist in the tale arises when Jon Wik enters the love story and creates a chaos.

Story about Military Naidu fights with his parents and brings his sisters son Karthik after her death. He becomes everything for Karthik takes care of him from childhood onwards. As time passes by Karthik falls in love with Haarika. This does not go well with her dad played by Rao Ramesh. He creates a small dispute between the Mama and Alludu and gets them divided. But the actual reason for Miltary Naidus rift with his Alludu is something else.
staring: Raashi Khanna, Naga Chaitanya Akkineni, Venkatesh

movieDescription: Movie story start with Valmiki is a small time employee in a big company. During his son’s birth his boss’s wife also gives birth to a baby boy. But upset with his financial status Valmiki cleverly interchanges the babies and brings the boss’s baby to his house and raises him. As time passes by a tragic turn around of events happen and the truth is out in the open.

Movie start with Chandu is a software engineer who falls in love with Swathi. Just when they decide to marry things take a u-turn and the couple finds out that Chandu has a problem with his horoscope and can get killed at any moment. To avoid this, they approach a Swamiji who orders for a special pooja. Just when they happen to go for this pooja Chandu gets involved in a scam featuring a minister.
staring: Sudigali Sudheer, Dhanya Balakrishnan, Ravi Kale

movieDescription: Movie stat with Ajay is a daring military officer who works for the Indian army. On the other hand, Bharati is a sincere professor in the city of Kurnool. She gets into a problem with a local minister played by Prakash Raj who plans to kill her. Right when she and her family are going to be killed, Ajay lands in Kurnool and saves her.

Movie is committed to shine well in the filmy world Srinivasa Reddy along with his friends Shakalaka Shankar and Satya try their luck in short films. In this process, they come across a drug-dealing gang and entangle themselves badly with the drug mafia.

Movie start in 208 A.D. in the Han Dinasty of China the tyrannic and greedy Prime Minster Cao Cao forces the reluctant Emperor Han to declare war against the kingdoms of Liu Bei and Sun Quan in the South of China. Cao Cao heads with a mighty army of one million soldiers and attacks Liu Bei. His advisor and war strategist Zhuge Liang heads to South in a diplomatic mission trying to convince Sun Quan to join force with Liu Bei against the powerful warlord.
staring: Tony Chiu-Wai Leung, Takeshi Kaneshiro, Fengyi Zhang

movieDescription: Expert assassin Henry Brogan is hiding out in a field as he awaits his target suspected terrorist Valery Dormov to pass by on a moving train. Just as Henry gets ready, his spotter and fellow DIA agent, Marino informs him that there is a little girl standing in front of Dormov. They must wait until she is out of sight, allowing Henry to take the shot.
staring: Will Smith, Mary Elizabeth Winstead, Clive Owen

movieDescription: Movie about Christmas Eve Angela Bridges, an ambitious young executive works late before she leaves for her family’s holiday party. When she gets down to the parking garage, she discovers that her car won’t start. Her garage is deserted and her cell phone doesn’t get a signal underground. When Thomas, a friendly security guard, comes along and offers to help, Angela nervously accepts his gesture of good will.
staring: Rachel Nichols, Wes Bentley, Simon Reynolds

movieDescription: Film start picking up one day after the events of the first part Paul wakes up in the creek surrounded by bloody water. He is severely infected by the mysterious flesh-disolving virus and he is covered in sores and boils. He begins walking through the forest as his skin begins to fall off.
staring: Rider Strong, Noah Segan, Alexi Wasser

movieDescription: Movie is about during a party in the Theta-Pi sorority house the sister Megan plays a prank with her unstable boyfriend Garrett simulating an OD after using pills. Her sisters Jessica, Claire, Ellie, Cassidy and Garrett’s sister Chugs suggest to dump her “body” in a lake and the stressed Garrett sticks the tire iron through the Megan’s chest killing her.
staring: Briana Evigan, Rumer Willis, Carrie Fisher

movieDescription: Movie story about Time travel always changes the present. When a group of archeologists go back to 1357 on a rescue mission they find themselves in the middle of a war between the English and the French troops. They try to return to the present safely altogether.
staring: Gerard Butler, Paul Walker, Billy Connolly

movieDescription: Movie is about Raghupathi Venkaiah Naidu born in the year 1887 at Machilipatnam of AP is widely regarded as father of Telugu Cinema and is an art enthusiast from an early age. He travels to Madras to pursue photography and what turns him into a pioneer of Telugu cinema is what the story is all about.
staring: Maharshi Raghava, Naresh Vijay Krishna, Tanikella Bharani

movieDescription: Movie start with Raghu a Btech student falls in love with Lekha who comes to his college for her films shoot. On the other hand Lekha is an orphan who is being taken care of by her wicked uncle Setu Veera Swamy. After a point Lekha runs away with Raghu and starts living happily. This does not go well with Veera Swamy and he causes a right between the couple and separates them. After four years, Lekha is found in Mumbai and is saved by Raghu’s brother Guru.
